        <h4 class="section-title">About Us</h4>
        <p style="text-align: justify; font-size: 19px;">
            Welcome to <strong>La Table by Cassandra and Sofia</strong>, where we bring the essence of French dining to your table.
            The story began with Cassandra and Sofia, two childhood friends from the Philippines who bonded over their shared passion
            for French cuisine and culture. During their travels to France, they fell in love with its rich culinary traditions, from
            buttery croissants to the elegance of charcuterie boards. Inspired, they dreamed of bringing this unique dining experience
            to their Filipino community, blending French sophistication with the warmth of Filipino hospitality. The name <strong>La Table</strong>,
            which means "The Table" in French, symbolizes a place where people come together to share good food, stories, and moments. Through their
            restaurant, Cassandra and Sofia aim to create a welcoming space where guests can experience the magic of French cuisine. It is
            their way of celebrating the connection between food and friendship, just as they have done throughout their lives.
        </p>

